data.description: Located in the Wescott Chase section of Wecott Plantation of Summerville and built in 2019. Enter into a two story foyer that opens up to the family room. Open floor plan with the kitchen & dining space overlooking the family room all with laminate wood flooring.  The kitchen features granite countertop, stainless steel appliances & pantry. Eat in kitchen space connects the interior space & the screened in porch. Fully fenced in backyard with patio. Upstairs to a small loft area & into the spacious master suite with a walk-in closet, &  dual sink vanity in bathroom. Two additional bedrooms w/ full bathroom in the hallway & laundry room on the 2nd floor. Close proximity to the well sought after Dorchester District II schools & large employers such as Boeing, Bosch, & Joint Base Charleston.
